Package magellan.client.utils

Class BookmarkManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • magellan.client.utils.BookmarkManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ShortcutListener, SelectionListener, EventListener, GameDataListener
    public class BookmarkManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements ShortcutListener, SelectionListener, GameDataListener
    Manages setting an getting of Bookmarks.
    - CTRL + F2 : place a bookmark on the current activeObject or removes it if already bookmarked
    - F2 : go to next bookmark
    - Shift + F2 : go to prior bookmark
    Author:
    Ulrich Küster
